name: Which Squad Member Are You?
overview: This Quiz will tell you which of the Elite 11 (one of 13 possibilities) members you are, based on your everyday actions, likenesses, and preferences. Warning, if you get any of these guys please remain calm and call the suicide hotline at 1-800-273-8255.

questions.title: Question 1
questions.question: You come home after a long day of classes and realize you're in the hip hop mood. Who are you most likely listening to?

questions.title: Question 2
questions.question: When you’ve got a project/test/assignment that you need to work on/study for, which of the following is most likely your go to study spot?

choices.D: I think I’m just gonna do it at home

questions.title: Question 3
questions.question: You're feeling hungry and don't feel like cooking, what are you most likely getting to eat tonight?

questions.title: Question 4
questions.question: Everyone is huddled on the sofa trying to figure out what show to watch. What show are you pitching?

choices.D: Screw that Imma go read a book

questions.title: Question 5
questions.question: Fast forward 5 years from now, you’ve graduated from college (hopefully iA) and you open up your garage, what car do you see?

choices.D: Honda Odyssey/ Toyota Sienna - something I can fit hella people in

questions.title: Question 6
questions.question: You’re back home for the week, and your parents spring the “when are you getting married” question.  What do you tell them?

choices.A: I just gotta finish up college and it's a done deal
choices.B: Mama give me a couple years until I'm financially stable
choices.C: Baba I just gotta find the right one, I’ll wait till the time is right
choices.D: Actually guys… the Nikah is next week, here’s your invitation

questions.title: Question 7
questions.question: It’s Thursday night and there are no Friday classes tomorrow. You look at your bois. What’s the move?

choices.A: This is a good chance to catch up on work
choices.B: Bro - we gotta go to MUGS
choices.C: Let’s go to Maple/Foxridge/Pack and watch a movie
choices.D: Ayy lets make this Florida Trip

questions.title: Question 8
questions.question: A friend borrows your laptop and goes on to Youtube. What is most likely found on your recommended videos?

choices.A: Sports Center Top 10 plays of the week
choices.D: Best Freestyle of the Year: King Los Kills the 5 Fingers of Death

questions.title: Question 9
questions.question: Your friends never seem to learn their lessons, so when your boi leaves their facebook wide open, what are you doing?

choices.A: Close it, no one messes with your mans
choices.B: Comment on and like other peoples photos
choices.C: Confess their love to someone through DMs
choices.D: Announce to the entire world that they’re getting engaged to some MSA person without telling either of them

questions.title: Question 10
questions.question: You’ve got a test for an important class tomorrow and it’s 9:00 pm, what you doing?

choices.A: You’re good, you’ve studied for a week
choices.B: Looks like youve got an all nighter ahead of you
choices.C: Too late to study now, what is the move fellas?
choices.D: I’m straight, just gotta find an open seat next to a smart-looking Asian
